last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 5
last_episode_to_air.overview: Carmo cold-bloodedly murders Dani after being exposed by her. Confusing him with Nando, the Albanians mistakenly kill Ionut, Cesáreo's new disciple. Unable to fulfill his commitment to Quesada, Muro immolates himself by throwing himself off a cliff. Gathered at the summit with Diosdado, Gema and Joao die in an exchange of gunfire.

name: Silent Cargo
overview: November 2019. A semi-submersible loaded with three tons of cocaine is seized off the Galician coast after having crossed the Atlantic. The captain, Nando, a promising young amateur boxer, travels accompanied by a Brazilian mechanic and a Colombian hitman. Three strangers locked up for almost a month in a claustrophobic handmade boat.

Nando will embark on a race against time, not only to recover the lost credit from those who trusted him but also to evade the police who have been on his trail for months.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Nando is a young Galician with a simple life. His perseverance leads him to win the amateur boxing contest but his ambition does not stop there, the reunion with his childhood friends leads him to make a series of bad decisions that will change his future forever.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Nando and Sergio arrive in Brazil, look at the boat in which they will do their new job and realize that luck is not on their side. The pursuit of Carmo and Ortiz continues.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: The adventures begin inside the semi-submersible. The crew members of the artifact encounter breakdowns, hunger, storms, etc. A news from Colombia will make everything more difficult for the protagonists. Carmo and Ortiz are getting closer to capturing them.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: The protagonists arrive in Galicia, the tension increases while the protagonists try to sink the semi-submersible to flee from the police.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Nando has been now for two years in jail where he is feared and loved. Meanwhile Valdés has certain issues to introduce the cocaine João sends, Ortiz is ready to give up on his investigation.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: After the unexpected and tragic death of Samu, the situation inside the jail is extremly tense, Nando is fearing for his life and must make a radical decision in order to save his life.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: After the arrest of a cocaine shipment, Sigüenza and Anxo enter the prison from which Nando has just escaped. Cesáreo tries to help Nando to redirect his life, but his plans are different.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Nando continues to advance with his plan while Valdés plunges towards defeat. Nando proposes a deal to Gema to bring Muro's fentalin while he begins to doubt Nando's honesty.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Nando has taken over the fentanyl truck, he is looking for a distributor, while Joao and Carlitos Miranda look for him. After all there must always be a king.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Nando, a young boxing promise gets involved in a drug traffic operation across the Atlantic with two unknown individuals.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: The theft of a truck loaded with fentanyl, orchestrated by a group of Albanians hired by the fragile alliance between Muro and the Boza-Merino tandem, puts Fernando Barreira in the difficult situation of having to be accountable to Diosdado. After numerous hardships, Nando manages to recover the truck. However, Carlitos Miranda has decided to change the rules of the game.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Fearing for his life, Muro self-inflicts injuries in prison. After escaping to the hospital, he forms an alliance with the Albanians. Miranda is pressured by Quesada, the cartel leader. It is revealed that Gema Valdés did not die and is undergoing rehabilitation after months in a coma. Nando proposes to Diosdado to increase their profits by bringing drugs via submarine, but he needs a partner:

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: With the help of Andrea, a young narco boat manufacturer, Nando facilitates Joao's escape. Muro and the Albanians kidnap Miranda. Gema tries to make a living as an honest citizen, while the 'marriage' of Boza-Merino begins to falter thanks to the cunning of Anxo. Muro swears to Quesada to defend the cartel's interests in Galicia.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: The drugs arrive in Galicia in two semi-submersibles, leaving Dani and her new partner, Lieutenant Novoa, powerless. The Diosdado-Joao-Nando triumvirate debuts successfully. In prison, Anxo assassinates Merino on Boza's orders. Muro orders the Albanians to issue a 'search and capture' order for Barreira. Dani is suspended from her duties by Carmo due to the judge Andrade's inaction.
